58738.title: Telemann - Cantate: Ich danke dem Herrn..TVWV 7:14

55726.title: Telemann - Cantate: Ich danke dem Herrn..TVWV 7:14
55726.description: Patrick Debrabandere leads the Vox Mago chamber choir in a performance of Georg Philipp Telemann's (1681-1767) cantata "Ich danke dem Herrn von ganzem Herzen" (TVWV 7:14). Recorded at the Klein Begijnhof, Gent, Belgium in December 2018 as part of the program In Tempus Adventus.
